    Serializable, HasCopy, AbstractSWE, AbstractSWEIdentifiable, BlockComponent, DataArray, DataComponent, DataStream, IDataConsumer, IDataProvider, ISweInputDataStream, ISweOutputDataStream

    public class SWEData
extends DataList
implements ISweInputDataStream, ISweOutputDataStream

    Implementation of SWE input/output data stream storing data in memory, This class also contains methods for parsing/writing the stored data.

    Since:
    Feb 21, 2007
